venue.name: The Café at The Governor's Inn

item.description:
Hi Trailblazers join us every Sunday for some good old "Bluegrass", Blues, Acustic, Country and Folk music at the Governors Inn, bring a lawn chair, sip something nice and cold and enjoy the music.  I will be bringing some games to play as we listen to the music. See you there!

The band starts playing 4 to 7 pm, it's Free but they do pass the "hat" around so if you like the band and want to donate that great!

See you there!

Peter
